Hello everyone, this is Shannon. I know I haven't been very active on Instagram lately, but I've been thinking about creating more content to show you how I do iPad lettering. I've been asked by people about which brushes I use for my iPad lettering, and I've been meaning to share this Procreate brush with you for free. I finally uploaded it onto my website now, and I named it 'Tulip' because of its oval-shaped attribute. 

Please go download it at www.fourwetfeet.com/learn or click on the link on my profile.

There will also be some iPad lettering guide sheets coming soon, so please stay tuned! I hope you enjoy this free brush, and please let me know if you have any questions. Love you all and thanks for following my creative journey. ✌️💕
